    helpText: 'Organizing critical financial information in one accessible location protects your family and simplifies financial management during emergencies. Create a secure binder or digital folder containing account numbers, emergency contacts for all financial institutions, beneficiary information, and basic access instructions for trusted family members. This preparation ensures your financial affairs can be managed quickly during medical emergencies or other crises while giving you peace of mind that your important information is organized and accessible.'
