    helpText: 'Setting up consistent retirement contributions through automatic transfers ensures you\'re building long-term wealth while reducing your current taxable income. Contact your employer\'s HR department to enroll in or increase your 401(k) contributions, or set up automatic monthly transfers to an IRA if self-employed. Even starting with a small percentage of your income creates a powerful foundation for compound growth and helps establish the habit of paying yourself first before other expenses.'
